    "description": "Embark on a unique adventure in Starwulf, where classic brick puzzle mechanics meet intense space shooter action. This innovative blend offers a fresh experience for puzzle enthusiasts and space shooter fans alike. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDelve into procedurally generated brick planets and explore randomly selected star systems, ensuring each gameplay session is a unique challenge. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs your experience grows, unlock special stages launched as missions, offering new gameplay events ranging from asteroid fields to enemy fleet attacks. Upgrade your ship to be prepared for more hostile planets.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe main game follows story line where the fate of players home planet hangs in the balance. Can you be the underdog who strikes back? <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt is also possible to play casually with subgames consisting of main stages of the game.",
